# shadcn UI Standards

This project uses **shadcn UI** for all UI elements.

## Initialization

If shadcn UI is not initialized in the project:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

## Adding Components

To install a specific component (example with button):

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

## Usage Guidelines

- ✅ Use shadcn UI components for all UI elements
- ✅ Install missing components using `npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>`
- ✅ Check if component exists before installing
- ❌ Don't create custom UI components when shadcn provides them

## Common Components

```bash
# Forms
npx shadcn@latest add button
npx shadcn@latest add input
npx shadcn@latest add form
npx shadcn@latest add select

# Layout
npx shadcn@latest add card
npx shadcn@latest add dialog
npx shadcn@latest add sheet

# Feedback
npx shadcn@latest add toast
npx shadcn@latest add alert
```
